ifconfig means interface configuration
It is used to configure a network interface


fokhrul@fokhrul-VirtualBox:~/Desktop$ ifconfig      ;Shows the network interfaces.
                                                    ; eth means ethernet connection(wired connection)

fokhrul@fokhrul-VirtualBox:~/Desktop$ ifconfig eth0       ;Shows eth0 interface only

fokhrul@fokhrul-VirtualBox:~/Desktop$ sudo ifconfig eth0 down     ;eth0 will go down

fokhrul@fokhrul-VirtualBox:~/Desktop$ sudo ifconfig eth0 up       ;eth0 is up now

